name: Cryptocurrency world
description: The future is changing, there is a new world now. Our lives, habits, thoughts, goals, knowledge and memories are changing. In short, humanity has stepped into a new world and a new life, and now everything is changing. The past is really a thing of the past. It's time to make room for cryptocurrencies in humanity's memory. It seems that this recent revolution will take its place in the memory of humanity for a long time and will not be erased...
